{"id":649,"date":"2020-11-10T17:29:14","date_gmt":"2020-11-10T22:29:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/?p=649"},"modified":"2020-11-12T09:03:53","modified_gmt":"2020-11-12T14:03:53","slug":"beginnings","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/beginnings\/","title":{"rendered":"Beginnings&#8230;"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>6 November 2020<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>This is an excerpt from a letter that went out to family and friends in early September 2020, announcing my decision to establish a Life Coaching practice.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>9 September 2020<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Greetings!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Praying this finds you in good health and surprised often by Joy, sailing the fair winds and following seas of God&#8217;s love and mercy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As part of my ongoing professional growth and development I am working toward certification as a Life Coach through Coaches Training Alliance (CTA) and credentialing by the International Coaching Federation (ICF). In July I officially began CTA\u2019s six-month intensive course of studies, with the goal of launching <strong><em>Synergy Life Coaching<\/em><\/strong> before the end of the year. Thanks to technology, I will be able to serve clients both locally and around the world from right here in St. Augustine, Florida.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Becoming a Life Coach is a natural use of my professional training, education, and life experience. I am not retiring from the priesthood, nor am I rejecting my identity or calling. . .  .  Life Coaching opens the door for my professional and personal growth in service to others and is in harmony with all God has done and is doing in our lives.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just in case you are wondering if there is anything you can do to be a part of this endeavor, you have some options:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Continue to intercede for us in prayer. All that happens of eternal value is a result of our prayers. Prayer manifests Reality, \u201con earth as it is in heaven.\u201d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;Volunteer yourself or refer a friend for a 50-minute <em>Sample Coaching Session<\/em> with me (no fee\/no obligation). This would help me fulfill one of my certification requirements and give you an opportunity to experience the potentially powerful dynamic of Life Coaching.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can imagine, I have a special interest in serving Christian clergy and missionaries.&nbsp; Thanks to the generosity of others, I will be able to offer them a reduced rate when needed.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To all of you who have lovingly both sailed and anchored with us over the years, we are forever grateful! \u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Fr. David<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ringthebells5x7-731x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-651\" width=\"533\" height=\"746\" srcset=\"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ringthebells5x7-731x1024.png 731w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ringthebells5x7-214x300.png 214w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ringthebells5x7-768x1075.png 768w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ringthebells5x7-1097x1536.png 1097w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ringthebells5x7-1463x2048.png 1463w, https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ringthebells5x7.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" \/><figcaption>From <em>Anthem<\/em>, in Stanger Music (permission requested from Random House)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>6 November 2020 This is an excerpt from a letter that went out to family and friends in early September 2020, announcing my decision to establish a Life Coaching practice. 9 September 2020 Greetings! Praying this finds you in good health and surprised often by Joy, sailing the fair winds and following seas of God&#8217;s [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/649"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=649"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/649\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1002,"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/649\/revisions\/1002"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=649"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=649"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/synergylife.coach\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=649"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}